--- title: Multi Core LR Find XLA Extensions keywords: fastai sidebar: home_sidebar summary: "Classes to replace LRFinder and patches to Learner" description: "Classes to replace LRFinder and patches to Learner" nb_path: "nbs/03d_multi_core.lr_find.ipynb" ---

{% endraw %}

Modifications to existing callback LRFinder are needed in order to run lr_find using multiple TPU cores. An equivalent xla_lr_find method is patched to Learner so it can run on multiple TPU cores.
